results.description:
Nebula has the Infinity Gauntlet -- and, in the most shocking twist yet,
Thanos now stands with Earth's heroes to defeat her! Can one being
possibly contain all that power? And if not Thanos, then who? With a
shock ending that'll leave you begging for more!
